.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL_SPENDABLE_KURTOSIS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-spendable-kurtosis \- FEAT-2815 kurtosis of spendable_msat across channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-spendable-kurtosis
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the kurtosis of spendable_msat across channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2815).
.PP
Output: JSON object with key \fBspendable_kurtosis\fR and \fBcount\fR.
Returns \fBnull\fR when fewer than the required minimum samples are available.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning (1)
